Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: fiftyone-pipeline-engines
info.summary: The 51Degrees Pipeline API is a generic web request intelligence and data processing solution with the ability to add a range of 51Degrees and/or custom plug ins (Engines). This package extends the flow element class created by the fiftyone.pipeline.core pacakge into a specialized type of flow element called an engine.
